s always - now you go to that park you dare. And there was a girl U used to play with, Lizzie Archer, and when we come out of school she'd say, come on, one swing and then we'll go home. But we won't tell anybody. I'd say sometimes, oh I can't - I daren't
. Oh. Oh, well come on, one. Well we'd have one - she'd have one, I'd have one then both run home.
