My sisters would - they probably would those days and - but even Sir those days weren't much - not like they are today like are they. If they were Sir well in those days they were somebody big were they not. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4790751 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid875679\charrsid5915590 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents in that way?
