ou but dark days and that, you know, very dark they'd come up, well somebody would come for you, but no, we went on our own. It was - you weren't frightened of anybody those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4790751 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid875679\charrsid5915590 Where did you have your mid-day meal?
