No, I liked it. The only thing was I had scarlet fever. And - little girl next door apparently had it and I - the lady asked me to go in and play with her - me mother didn't know she had it. And - I had it worse than her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4790751 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid875679\charrsid5915590 What did you feel about the teachers?
